He love from his breakfast-nook beach
and came into the livingroom, where
Heather and neve nood aglan al
lis enhance. He came, alon talling
forved in a ungainly sluttle, neck
lliun ou, and dangling loosely.
Then, abruptly, le diew like self up
and walked a the very lips of
lis bes. He shielded lis aus
One his lead and youned agaped,
diawing-ic gied luealls lla
became goal righs of ecrasy.
